txt.en: Destroyed many corrupt runes in Râkh Mathán.
Corrupt runes can be found in Râkh Mathán in Rath Dúath.\n\nYou should destroy corrupt runes in Râkh Mathán.
You have done much to discourage the Wargs from remaining in the hills of Râkh Mathán. Those who fight for Gondor to cleanse the Morgul Vale will surely thank you for your efforts on their behalf.

The hillside at Râkh Mathán is home to many Wargs. The dens are protected by corrupted runes placed there by the Orcs to protect the lands they claim for their own. These runes should be destroyed or the Wargs will quickly return to Râkh Mathán, and the Morgul Vale will never be free of them.
Corrupt runes can be found in Râkh Mathán in Rath Dúath.\n\nYou should destroy corrupt runes in Râkh Mathán.
Warg dens litter the hills of the Rath Dúath, but the wargs are not alone. Orcs have bred and trained the beasts to follow their master's lash.
